egory 1: Basics (15 Programs)
Print "Hello, World!"

print("Hello, World!")
Find the sum of two numbers.

a = int(input("Enter first number: "))
b = int(input("Enter second number: "))
print("Sum:", a + b)
Find the area of a circle.

radius = float(input("Enter radius: "))
area = 3.14 * radius ** 2
print("Area of circle:", area)
